{"tid":1815201,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派有咩理由要抗拒香港獨立？","createTime":"2020-01-07T10:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:12:45.000Z","uid":20454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27a7c1d0a1429100e853383ab6e9e2e74b77b2ac","tid":1815201,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">&ldquo;中國人的性情是總喜歡調和、折中的。譬如你說，這個屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不容許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。&rdquo;（魯迅）</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們反逃犯條例修訂，為了維護香港法治<br />\n我們要推動真普選，因為我們維護基本法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果港共唔肯開窗點算？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為了光明，拆屋頂就是義務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有普選，唯有獨立</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28d5c1653a687c44932da9b4f52eacb1176d9f5","tid":1815201,"uid":133519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"為利益"},{"pid":"649204f65fdb91bdeccd789236bb8e697e178758","tid":1815201,"uid":45466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27a7c1d0a1429100e853383ab6e9e2e74b77b2ac","tid":1815201,"uid":20454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">&ldquo;中國人的性情是總喜歡調和、折中的。譬如你說，這個屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不容許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。&rdquo;（魯迅）</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們反逃犯條例修訂，為了維護香港法治<br />\n我們要推動真普選，因為我們維護基本法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果港共唔肯開窗點算？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為了光明，拆屋頂就是義務</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有普選，唯有獨立</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"